WHAT IT DOES?
=============
This test package is used to test Android widgets. It's based on Android's
widget test cases with additional test cases developed by MediaTek.


HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
$ mmm vendor/mediatek/proprietary/frameworks/base/tests/widget


HOW TO USE IT?
==============
After installing this test package, run the test cases by using ADB.

To run all of the test cases in this test package, execute:

$ adb shell am instrument -w com.mediatek.common.widget.tests/android.test.InstrumentationTestRunner

To run all of the test cases in the class ActionBarActionModeListTest, execute:

$ adb shell am instrument --no-window-animation -w -e class com.mediatek.common.widget.tests.ActionBarActionModeListTest com.mediatek.common.widget.tests/android.test.InstrumentationTestRunner

For more information about how to run test cases by using ADB, please refer to 

http://developer.android.com/tools/testing/testing_otheride.html#RunTestsCommand

